FRONTLINE ROADS v0.30.3 COMPACT FACILITY PANEL AUDIT

Release: 0.30.3-compact-defense-panel

Functional corrections
- Facility summary no longer renders the next-tier comparison by default.
- Description replaces the summary rather than expanding underneath it.
- Upgrade comparison replaces the summary and requires a separate confirmation action.
- Opening upgrade information does not mutate resources or facility state.
- Facility panel mode survives live HUD rerenders.
- Selecting a different object resets the facility panel to summary.
- Tapping the selected facility again or empty map space closes the panel.
- Existing repair, gate conversion and two-step removal flows remain connected.

Layout boundaries
- Portrait summary maximum: 30vh / 250px.
- Details and upgrade maximum: 34vh / 300px.
- Context content scrolls independently from the always-visible action row.
- Landscape facility inspection uses a compact right-side panel.
- Upgrade deltas remain a two-column grid on phone widths.

